  "reference_number": "RUS1717",
  "remarks": "\nReza Khaki is an involved person under the \nRussia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 in that he is a Board Member of Qods Aviation Industry Company (QAI), a subsidiary of Iran Aviation Industries Organisation (IAIO), which has provided or made available Unmanned Aerial Vehicles (UAVs) for use by the Russian military that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty, or independence of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
